  "claim_short": "Counterexample to the unnormalized alpha=1 homogeneous weighted Minkowski extension left open in Remark 2.25 of arXiv:2111.10923. For the planar 1-homogeneous measure dmu(x)=|x|^{-1} dx, no symmetric convex body K has dS_K^mu = 2 dtheta. Support function equation h+h''=a sqrt(h^2+(h')^2) reduces via y=h'/h to an autonomous ODE, whose periodic solutions force a=1.",
